<h3>Adding expenses</h3>
<p>
  Adding expenses or extra income should be simple. This behavior should feel seamless and effortless to users. Hence, I wanted to simplify and condesne some of the steps and provide visual queus with colors.
</p>
<video src="/static/img/projects/budget/adding_expense.mov" controls></video>
<p>
  Tap the minus button (or the plus for extra income) and choose from the default categories, such as coffee, groceries, gas, and others. These categories can be edited and users can add new categories.
</p>
<p>
  Then, enter the amount spent. Notes can be added for more detailed categorization.
</p>
<p>Entered activities are listed by time and color-coded based on the category.</p>

