<h3>Connecting with other devices</h3>
<p>
  One of the core features of the design was connecting and syncing data with other devices. There are two ways to connect: duplicate your data to another device or retrieve data from a different device.
</p>

<video src="/static/img/projects/budget/connect_01.mov" controls></video>

<p>
  <b>Copy and share your budget</b><br>
  A passcode will be generated for connecting with other devices. This code can be sent via messages and must be entered on the designated device to duplicate and retrieve data.
</p>
<img src="/static/img/projects/budget/budget-3-connecting.png" alt="Copy and share your budget">
